reviewText: I was a Extra in this movie, & had given up hope of ever seeing it again. I played a reporter sitting at my desk, in the newsroom scene. The movie wasn't that good, but its fun seeing how I looked so many years ago. Thanks Amazon !!
My parents were the uncredited EMT's
Corny. Only bought because I was an extra in this movie.
Movie was very watchable since Adam West was in it...nothing great but I mostly wanted the movie because it was shot in my neighborhood.
I bought this movie purely for the fact that my friend played the murderer. The story seem to place too much attention to the side story and rushed the plot.
